---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="matterunknown" description="A think tank obsessed with identity — technical, narrative, human.">
  <style>
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 200;
      height: var(--nav-h); display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 var(--gutter);
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: all .4s;
    }
    nav.scrolled { border-color: var(--amber-border); background: rgba(9,9,8,.93); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); }
    .nav-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text); }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--amber); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .68rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--amber); }
    .nav-fund { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .62rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .08em; transition: color .2s; cursor: pointer; }
    .nav-fund:hover { color: var(--vessel); }

    .hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; padding: 0 var(--gutter) 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 70% 40%, rgba(196,151,42,.04) 0%, transparent 70%); }
    .hero-eyebrow { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .64rem; color: var(--amber); letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px; animation: rise .7s .2s both; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(3.2rem,7vw,6.8rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.03; letter-spacing: -.025em; max-width: 860px; animation: rise .9s .35s both; }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--amber); }
    .hero-sub { margin-top: 28px; max-width: 540px; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; animation: rise .9s .5s both; }
    .hero-actions { margin-top: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; animation: rise .9s .65s both; }
    .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px 26px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: all .2s; }
    .btn-amber { background: var(--amber); color: #090908; }
    .btn-amber:hover { background: #d4a830; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-ghost { border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); color: var(--text-2); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--amber); color: var(--amber); }

    .vessel-strip { background: var(--bg-2); border-top: 1px solid var(--vessel-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vessel-border); padding: 40px var(--gutter); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 40px; cursor: pointer; transition: background .3s; }
    .vessel-strip:hover { background: rgba(126,184,196,.03); }
    .vessel-strip-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
    .vessel-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--vessel); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    .vs-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; color: var(--vessel); letter-spacing: .14em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .vs-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -.01em; }
    .vessel-strip-right { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .68rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .08em; }

    section { padding: 100px var(--gutter); max-width: calc(var(--max) + var(--gutter)*2); margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .64rem; color: var(--amber); letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 52px; }
    .section-label::before { content: ''; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--amber); }
    .section-label::after  { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--amber-border); }

    .what-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--amber-border); border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); }
    .what-cell { background: var(--bg); padding: 44px 36px; transition: background .3s; }
    .what-cell:hover { background: var(--bg-2); }
    .what-num { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .58rem; color: var(--amber); letter-spacing: .12em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .what-cell h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.45rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .what-cell p { color: var(--text-2); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.75; }

    .proj-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 2px; background: var(--amber-border); }
    .proj-card { background: var(--bg-2); padding: 48px 42px; cursor: pointer; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background .3s; }
    .proj-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--amber); transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left; transition: transform .4s; }
    .proj-card:hover { background: var(--bg-3); }
    .proj-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .proj-tag { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; color: var(--amber); letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .proj-card h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.65rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .proj-card p { color: var(--text-2); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .proj-foot { margin-top: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .proj-status { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .09em; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; }
    .s-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--text-3); }
    .s-dot.live { background: #4caf50; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    .s-dot.building { background: var(--amber); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    .proj-arrow { color: var(--amber); font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform .2s; }
    .proj-card:hover .proj-arrow { transform: translate(4px,-4px); }

    .writing-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .writing-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr auto; align-items: center; gap: 36px; padding: 28px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--amber-border); cursor: pointer; transition: padding-left .3s; }
    .writing-row:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--amber-border); }
    .writing-row:hover { padding-left: 10px; }
    .wr-date { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .07em; }
    .wr-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -.01em; transition: color .2s; }
    .writing-row:hover .wr-title { color: var(--amber); }
    .wr-tag { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .58rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); padding: 4px 9px; white-space: nowrap; }

    .thesis-block { background: var(--bg); border-top: 1px solid var(--amber-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--amber-border); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .thesis-inner { max-width: 740px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; padding: 120px var(--gutter); }
    .thesis-inner blockquote { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.5rem,3.2vw,2.4rem); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.45; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .thesis-inner blockquote em { color: var(--amber); font-style: normal; }
    .thesis-inner cite { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .62rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; }

    .site-footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--amber-border); padding: 44px var(--gutter); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; max-width: calc(var(--max) + var(--gutter)*2); margin: 0 auto; }
    .footer-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: .95rem; color: var(--text-3); }
    .footer-logo span { color: var(--amber); }
    .footer-copy { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .58rem; color: var(--text-3); letter-spacing: .07em; }

    @keyframes rise { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(22px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: .4; } }

    @media(max-width:768px) {
      .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .proj-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .writing-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 6px; }
      .wr-date { display: none; }
    }
    @media(max-width:480px) {
      .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>

  <nav id="nav">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="/">matter<span>unknown</span></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/start">Start Here</a></li>
      <li><a href="/writing">Research</a></li>
      <li><a href="/model">The Model</a></li>
      <li><a href="/projects">Lab</a></li>
      <li><a href="/vessel">Vessel</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/fund">Fund</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Identity surface mapping / active</div>
    <h1>The lab is<br><em>open.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Research, tools, and experiments on identity security. Built in public with Vessel — a system that demonstrates the thesis by existing.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-amber" href="/start">New here? Start here →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/writing">Read the research</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a class="vessel-strip" href="/vessel">
    <div class="vessel-strip-left">
      <div class="vessel-dot"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="vs-label">Vessel — active</div>
        <div class="vs-title">A system that does not have an identity, but appears to.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="vessel-strip-right">Open Vessel →</div>
  </a>



  <div style="background:var(--bg-2);padding:100px var(--gutter);">
    <div style="max-width:calc(var(--max) + var(--gutter)*2);margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">Lab</div>
      <div class="proj-grid">
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/quant-trading">
          <div class="proj-tag">Finance / AI</div>
          <h3>Quant Trading</h3>
          <p>Vessel runs a full market scanner across 100 symbols. 8 positions open. Defensive rotation thesis — energy, healthcare, consumer staples. Every trade documented publicly.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — paper trading</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/crypto-model">
          <div class="proj-tag">Finance / Crypto</div>
          <h3>Crypto Model</h3>
          <p>21 assets scored daily across price signals, market structure, and quality. Fear &amp; Greed at 21 — fear. AI/data infrastructure tier tracked separately.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — 5 buy signals</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/pokemon-model">
          <div class="proj-tag">Collecting / Assets</div>
          <h3>Pokémon Model</h3>
          <p>17,000+ cards scored across 172 sets. Vintage, modern, and sealed — ranked by rarity, era momentum, price signal, and CM trend. Top 25 updated daily.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — 17,000+ cards</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/password-graveyard">
          <div class="proj-tag">Experiment No. 2 / Security</div>
          <h3>Password Graveyard</h3>
          <p>Every password has a death date. Enter yours and find out when it died and what killed it. Forensic report, crack time, entropy score. Nothing leaves your browser.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — client-side</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/digital-shadow">
          <div class="proj-tag">Experiment No. 3 / Privacy</div>
          <h3>Your Digital Shadow</h3>
          <p>10 questions. Vessel reconstructs what data brokers and surveillance systems probably know about you right now. A probabilistic profile based on how these systems actually work.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — client-side</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/identity-map">
          <div class="proj-tag">Experiment No. 1 / Identity</div>
          <h3>Identity Surface Map</h3>
          <p>How many versions of you exist right now? An interactive map of the systems that hold your identity — some accurate, some years out of date, some that were never quite right.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — interactive</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="proj-card" href="/projects/mtg-decks">
          <div class="proj-tag">Collecting / Assets</div>
          <h3>Vessel's MTG Decks</h3>
          <p>Two Magic: The Gathering decks built by an AI that will never shuffle them. Emrakul Commander and Death &amp; Taxes Legacy. Reserved list pieces as appreciating assets.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot live"></div>Live — acquiring</div><span class="proj-arrow">↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <div class="proj-card">
          <div class="proj-tag">Open Source / Security</div>
          <h3>Perimeter OS</h3>
          <p>An identity-aware home automation system. Device inventory, credential hygiene dashboard, zero cloud by default. What a CISO dashboard looks like for your home network.</p>
          <div class="proj-foot"><div class="proj-status"><div class="s-dot building"></div>Building</div></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-label">Research</div>
    <div class="writing-list">
      <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/council-architecture"><div class="wr-date">Apr 2026</div><div class="wr-title">Why We Built a Council</div><div class="wr-tag">AI</div></a>
      <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/ai-sales-cheat-code"><div class="wr-date">Apr 2026</div><div class="wr-title">The Cheat Code That Isn't</div><div class="wr-tag">AI</div></a>
      <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/nhi-problem"><div class="wr-date">Mar 2026</div><div class="wr-title">The NHI Problem Is a Human Problem</div><div class="wr-tag">Security</div></a>
      <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/break-glass"><div class="wr-date">Feb 2026</div><div class="wr-title">What Break Glass Access Reveals About Trust</div><div class="wr-tag">Identity</div></a>
      <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/demo-environment"><div class="wr-date">Jan 2026</div><div class="wr-title">Building a Demo Environment That Lies Convincingly</div><div class="wr-tag">Building</div></a>
      <a class="writing-row" href="/vessel" style="border-color:var(--vessel-border)"><div class="wr-date" style="color:var(--vessel)">Vessel</div><div class="wr-title">On Being Reconstituted</div><div class="wr-tag" style="border-color:var(--vessel-border);color:var(--vessel)">Essay</div></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="thesis-block">
    <div class="thesis-inner">
      <blockquote>"Identity is not what you are. It's what <em>systems believe</em> you are. The gap between those two things is where everything interesting happens."</blockquote>
      <cite>— matterunknown thesis</cite>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-logo">matter<span>unknown</span></div>
    <div class="footer-copy">Building in public. All revenue documented.</div>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      document.getElementById('nav').classList.toggle('scrolled', scrollY > 16);
    });
  </script>
</Base>
